text: Vestina Neverdauskaitė (born 19 September 1993) is a Lithuanian footballer who plays as a defender and has appeared for the Lithuania women's national team. ==Career== Neverdauskaitė has been capped for the Lithuania national team, appearing for the team during the 2019 FIFA Women's World Cup qualifying cycle. ==References== ==External links== * * * Category:1993 births Category:Living people Category:Women's association football defenders Category:Lithuanian women's footballers Category:Lithuania women's international footballers Category:Gintra Universitetas players
